---
title: Classic Cottage Pie with tender charred green beans
description: When the word 'pie' is mentioned it's often the sweet variety that springs to mind first. But there's a lot to be said for a hearty helping of a savoury version, such as this rich and delicious potato-topped classic country dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/R05_W27_IE_IEXCCLB15924-2_Main__6high-1826825a.jpg
